title: Mizzou basketball very deep at the guard position
text:
Mizzou basketball very deep at the guard position POSTED: 07:00 PM CDT Oct 18, 2015 UPDATED: 11:27 PM CDT Oct 18, 2015 
The Mizzou basketball team has 8 guards on this year's roster. Only 2 of them are upperclassmen. Hear from Coach Kim Anderson and freshman guard Terrence Phillips on the guard competition.
